    "game-id": "c023e39d1397a7e5ff47fe46622941f3",
    "spell_type": "focus",
    "rank": 4,
    "text": "You adopt the stance of clinging shadows. You can make shadow grasp Strikes. These deal 1d4 void damage; are in the brawling group; and have the agile, grapple, reach, and unarmed traits. While in clinging shadows stance, you gain a +2 circumstance bonus to Athletics checks to Grapple, and to the DC for creatures to Escape from you.",
